  <brief_title>Hepatitis C-Video vs. Brochure Education Delivery</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Study Showing the Effect of Video Interactive Education on Medical Decision Making in Patients on Opiate Replacement Therapy (ORT) With a History of Hepatitis C</official_title>
  <sponsors>
